Class DeliveryMarket

java.lang.Object
models.DeliveryMarket
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<DeliveryMarket>
public class DeliveryMarket extends Object implements Comparable<DeliveryMarket>
This class encapsulates the delivery market regions data. It holds information like name of the market region, total deliveries in that region, total number of late deliveries in that region and the proportion of late deliveries for that region.
